message.body: Hi, do you still have parking for Saturday available?
Will I be parked in? Or can I come and leave at anytime?
I can guarantee you can come and go at any time if you leave your keys (so I can keep your car at the end of the driveway).
Might be irrelevant depending on when you arrive.
Or you can have the entire driveway (2 cars) for $60.
I'm going to be arriving first thing in morning about 7 and leaving early evening most likely
If your comfortable leaving your keys and allowing me to move your vehicle, I can guarantee your car is in a position to leave at any time.
